==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unprovide
<hw>Un`pro*vide</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>provide</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of necessary
provision; to unfurnish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Lest her . . . beauty <qex>unprovide</qex> my mind again.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unprovident</ent>⟦br⟧
